
Macro DEFCOLLECTION

Syntax:
defcollection (inherited-class :accessor origin-class) {slot-description}* => structure-name

Arguments and Values:
inherited-class---a symbol.
accessor---a keyword.
origin-class---a symbol.
structure-name---a symbol.

Examples:
;; define original structure
 (defstruct node name)

;; define inherited collection structure
 (defcollection (nodes :set node))

;; define structure components records
 (defstruct graph
   (nodes nil :type nodes))

 (defparameter *nodes* nil)
 (push (make-node :name "node1") *nodes*)
 (push (make-node :name "node2") *nodes*)

 (make-graph :nodes (make-nodes :set (nreverse *nodes*)))

